Warm Greetings! ✨

Are you a budding techie, having interest towards UI/UX and graphic designing? Well then, you know we've always got your back!

Having said that, we are providing you the opportunity to pave your path towards being involved in the design process for the next hot gadget. 🤩

📢 Here's the complete roadmap from beginner to expert in UI/UX Design: 
📍 Complete Beginner start with the free course 'Innovation Through Design'.
(https://www.coursera.org/learn/innovation-through-design)

📍Followed by the 'Graphic Design Specialization Course' to make your grip over the subject stronger. (https://www.coursera.org/specializations/graphic-design)

📍Finally, 'UX Specialization Course from the University of Minnesota' is best suited to take you to the expert level. (https://www.coursera.org/specializations/user-interface-design)

Along with the aforementioned courses, do read this book by Steve Krug 📚:
https://www.pdfdrive.com/dont-make-me-think-revisited-e33494890.html

See you at the end of the journey 🏃‍♂️🏃🏻‍♀️💫

Thank you.
Regards, 
HITK Tech Community👩🏻‍💻👨🏻‍💻 
